== 設計 ==
'''澳大利亚国徽'''以盾牌為中心，盾面上的圖案代表組成聯邦的六個州<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.anbg.gov.au/oz/arms.html |title=Government of Australia: Department of the Environment and Water Resources |access-date=2014-02-13 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308153529/http://www.anbg.gov.au/oz/arms.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>：

